sentences.en: The dynamic LED lighting surface covering the undulating ceilings of the outdoor roof canopies gives the Busan Cinema Center its symbolic and representative iconographic feature.
sentences.cn: 室外屋顶檐篷起伏的天花板由动态LED照明表面覆盖，给予釜山电影中心的象征性和代表性的影像学特征。

sentences.en: Your iconographic views seem to be revolving around an image of a us marine on a skateboard!
sentences.cn: 你们关于肖像的观点好像是围绕着滑板上的美国海军的形象来谈的！

trans.tran_cn: 肖像的，肖像学的，图像材料的，图示法的象征
